LOTUS TURBO CHALLENGE II:

        When the game requests a password, type "TURPENTINE" to stop the
        clock.  Type "DEESIDE" to qualify even when you run out of time.
        type in "DUX" to play a familiar sub game.

                                 (LEVEL CODES)

            Night course--"TWILIGHT"        Fog course----"PEA SOUP"
            Snow course--"THE SKIDS"        Desert course--"PEACHES"
            Motor course-"LIVERPOOL"        Marsh course----"BAGLEY"
                              Storm course-"E BOW"

        Also try; DEESIDE ----- Goto next stage when you run out of time.
                  TURPENTINE -- The timer stays on ten seconds.

        If you enter the words MONSTER and SEVENTEEN (in the respective name
        slots) you'll discover a rather familiar game.
